Package assemblers

Class Assembler

java.lang.Object
assemblers.Assembler
Direct Known Subclasses:
ChamplainAssembler, MaisonneuveAssembler
public abstract class Assembler
extends java.lang.Object
This abstract class is used to assemble the CourseElements from the HtmlPages given. You need to extend this class and implement its methods. You will receive the Html page corresponding to the method you are using.
